issue.title: Nice work guys + leave it up?
issue.body:
So unfortunately [we didn't win](http://callout.city/callouts/56aea7fe5e63fdb01623183f) but that doesn't have to be the end.

How interested are you all in maintaining it? Usually these projects have a tendency to die off a bit after the main event. I personally would rather work on something else with you all, but am up for keeping up this project if we have a clear direction. 

Either way, as long as it's cool with Jerry, I say we leave it up for a while.

@zllovesuki @elanini @terminull
